6
00:00:46,159 --> 00:00:48,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nestala je break scena.

7
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,840
[SPEAKER_02] Je, da, nažalost, ti je malo.

8
00:00:50,799 --> 00:00:51,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ne radi tebe, ali.

9
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:54,079
[SPEAKER_02] Je, nije radi mene, malo si stišao, ali to sve je ono.

10
00:00:54,479 --> 00:00:54,960
[SPEAKER_02] Nažalost.

11
00:00:55,520 --> 00:01:01,439
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, opet je krenulo zadnjih godinu dana, nešto se počelo opet u Zagrebu, neke eventije, otvarati to.

12
