20
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,719
[SPEAKER_02] I onda su tam dečki plesali i to.

21
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:45,519
[SPEAKER_02] I ja gledam, mama daj tu, mama daj tu, ja bih, ja bih.

22
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,599
[SPEAKER_02] I tako sam krenuo, tako mi je to zanimalo.

23
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,920
[SPEAKER_02] Stara opisala, i eto ono.

24
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:53,280
[SPEAKER_02] Počio sam s tim četiri i pol godine, samo na promenadi plesu.

25
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:59,359
[SPEAKER_02] Tako se to razvilo, ali nisam htio dopustiti, ono, škola, ništa, samo break ono.

26
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] I došao break down, evo.

27
