37
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,199
[SPEAKER_02] Da, to je šteta.

38
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:38,479
[SPEAKER_02] I znači, počeo si tamo, imaš trenera.

39
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:44,479
