[SPEAKER_01] Da, mislim, to moraš voljeti.

107
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:26,240
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo živjeti, da.

108
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:27,279
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo živjeti, da.

109
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:30,240
[SPEAKER_01] Za još ćemo nabaviti jedan stiropor.

110
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:33,120
